---
import { Building2, Heart, Users, Target, Eye, Lightbulb } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section id="profile" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#F5F5F5] via-white to-[#F5F5F5] py-16 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden relative scroll-mt-20">
  <!-- Background decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-[#388E3C]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-[#81D4FA]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 max-w-7xl relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
      {/* Header Section */}
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        {/* Badge */}
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#388E3C]/10 rounded-full border border-[#388E3C]/20">
          <Building2 class="w-4 h-4 text-[#388E3C]" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-[#388E3C] uppercase tracking-wider">Profil Yayasan</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#388E3C] via-[#81D4FA] to-[#FFD700] bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight pb-1">Tentang Yayasan Sawiyan</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Yayasan Sawiyan adalah organisasi nirlaba yang berkomitmen untuk memberikan kontribusi positif bagi masyarakat melalui program-program sosial, kemanusiaan, dan keagamaan.</p>
      </div>

      {/* Content Grid */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        {/* Left Content */}
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Visi Kami</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Menjadi yayasan terdepan dalam memberikan kontribusi positif bagi masyarakat melalui program-program yang berkelanjutan dan berdampak luas.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Misi Kami</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#388E3C]/10 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                  <Heart class="w-4 h-4 text-[#388E3C]" />
                </div>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Menyelenggarakan program sosial untuk membantu masyarakat yang membutuhkan</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#81D4FA]/10 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                  <Users class="w-4 h-4 text-[#81D4FA]" />
                </div>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Mengembangkan program kemanusiaan yang berkelanjutan</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#FFD180]/10 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                  <Target class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FFD180]" />
                </div>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Meningkatkan kualitas hidup masyarakat melalui pendidikan dan pelatihan</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Right Image */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529156069898-49953e39b3ac?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Profil Yayasan Sawiyan" class="w-full h-[400px] object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#388E3C]/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          {/* Decorative Elements */}
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-24 h-24 bg-[#81D4FA]/20 rounded-full blur-xl hidden lg:block"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-[#FFD700]/20 rounded-full blur-xl hidden lg:block"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Visi Misi Cards Section */}
      <div id="visi-misi" class="scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4 mb-12">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#388E3C]/10 rounded-full border border-[#388E3C]/20">
            <Target class="w-4 h-4 text-[#388E3C]" />
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-[#388E3C] uppercase tracking-wider">Visi & Misi</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#388E3C] via-[#81D4FA] to-[#FFD700] bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight pb-1">Visi & Misi Yayasan Sawiyan</h2>
        </div>

        {/* Visi Misi Cards */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          {/* Visi Card */}
          <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
            {/* Decorative gradient accent */}
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#388E3C] to-[#81D4FA]"></div>

            {/* Icon */}
            <div class="mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#388E3C]/10 to-[#388E3C]/5 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Eye class="w-8 h-8 text-[#388E3C]" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Visi</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Menjadi yayasan terdepan dalam memberikan kontribusi positif bagi masyarakat melalui program-program yang berkelanjutan, inovatif, dan berdampak luas dalam bidang sosial, kemanusiaan, dan keagamaan.
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Misi Card */}
          <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
            {/* Decorative gradient accent */}
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#81D4FA] to-[#FFD180]"></div>

            {/* Icon */}
            <div class="mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#81D4FA]/10 to-[#81D4FA]/5 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Lightbulb class="w-8 h-8 text-[#81D4FA]" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Misi</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#388E3C] mt-2"></div>
                <span>Menyelenggarakan program sosial untuk membantu masyarakat yang membutuhkan</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#81D4FA] mt-2"></div>
                <span>Mengembangkan program kemanusiaan yang berkelanjutan dan berdampak positif</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#FFD180] mt-2"></div>
                <span>Meningkatkan kualitas hidup masyarakat melalui pendidikan dan pelatihan</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#FFD700] mt-2"></div>
                <span>Mengembangkan program keagamaan untuk memperkuat nilai-nilai spiritual</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#388E3C] mt-2"></div>
                <span>Membangun jaringan kerjasama dengan berbagai pihak untuk memperluas dampak program</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
